<h2>Data Source</h2>

<p>Fetches from <a href="https://relay.nostdlib.workers.dev/">https://relay.nostdlib.workers.dev/</a> which returns:</p>

<pre><code>{
  "clients": {
    "count": 1,
    "connections": [{ "id": "...", "ip": "...", "location": "...", "connectedAt": 0, "messageCount": 0, "relayed": false }]
  },
  "relays": {
    "count": 0,
    "connections": []
  }
}</code></pre>

<h2>Development</h2>

<pre><code># Run
dotnet run

# Or with hot reload
dotnet watch</code></pre>

<p>Starts on <code>http://localhost:5057</code> / <code>https://localhost:7104</code>.</p>

